Message: The user completes the submission of the form
My ad was initially rejected Ad Set ID:1901808462393495554

Hi Candis, I'm sorry to hear that your ad was rejected. To understand the specific reason for the rejection, please check your email for a message from Ad Support with the subject line ‘Urgent: Ad Rejected - Action Required.’ The email will provide details on why your ad was rejected and how you can fix it. Once you've made the necessary revisions, you can resubmit your ad. For more detailed guidance, you can refer to this article: [My ad got rejected. What's next?](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/18085960681101-My-ad-got-rejected-What-s-next). If you need further assistance, feel free to ask!
I did an appeal and they have now approved it
That's great to hear, Candis! I'm glad your appeal was successful and your ad has been approved. If you have any other questions or need further assistance, feel free to let me know!
BUT I had it set up to run last night at midnight

I understand your concern, Candis. Since your ad was approved after the scheduled start time, it might not have started running as planned. You can check the status of your ad in your News Break account to see if it's currently active or if you need to reschedule it. If you encounter any issues or need help rescheduling, please reach out to adsupport@newsbreak.com for assistance.
that box is greyed out and I can't change it

I'm sorry to hear that you're having trouble rescheduling your ad, Candis. Since the option is greyed out, I recommend reaching out directly to our support team for assistance. Please email adsupport@newsbreak.com with your Ad Set ID (1901808462393495554) and explain the issue you're facing. They should be able to help you get it sorted out quickly.
